title: 3br - *** ABSOLUTELY STUNNING ** COMPLETELY REBUILT**
posting_body: ['Gorgeous 3 Bedroom Apt.', 'Completely Renovated & Stunning 1870 Victorian Mansion, Amazing Location, 1 Block to Commuter Rail (11 minutes, nonstop directly to Boston), Large Sunny Rooms w 10 ft. ceilings, In House Laundry, New Bathroom, New Specialty Hardwood Floors, New X-Large Thermal Pane Designer Anderson Windows.', 'New; Heating & Central A/C, Electric, Kitchen w/ High End Maple Cabinets, stained 6 panel doors & trim, New Insulation (saves $$).', 'Deck w/ slider, Digital Security System, Disposal, Dishwasher, New High End Everything.', ' Even has a mudroom.', 'Central A/C is awesome in summer and New Natural Gas Heating System with all brand-new insulation and construction makes the apartment super-efficient to heat in winter.', ' Again, will save huge $$s.', 'Available w/ flexible move in date.', 'We also have move-in dates for Sept. 1st, 2022.', 'Just Beautiful!!', ' No Fees!']
